  <brief_title>Human Papilloma Virus (HPV) Knowledge and Attitudes and the Role of (SES) Socioeconomic Status and Ethnicity</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of Socioeconomic Status and Ethnicity in Influencing HPV Vaccine Knowledge and Attitudes in Adult Women</official_title>
